//////////////////////
Optional Prerequisites
//////////////////////

// Install NUnit 2 as seeing using dotnet 2, otherwise NUnit3 will be used.
sudo apt-get install nupkg-nunit.2.6.4

///////////////////
Creating a new test
///////////////////

// In <unit-test> folder

dotnet new classlib -f netcoreapp2.0
dotnet add package nunit
dotnet add package nunit3testadapter
dotnet add package microsoft.net.test.sdk

// In root test folder
dotnet sln add ./Tests/<unit-test>.Tests/<unit test>.Tests.csproj

// In <unit-test> folder

Add test to .cs file
Ensure it has a [TestFixture] and [Test]
dotnet test
